          .txt-box
            %p Many a times the word Destruction or Destroyer is taken in a negative light. Forever has the populus talked about Growth and Progress, but have we ever questioned Why, And till what end will we continue to grow. Sometimes it becomes necessary to stop and realise the repercussions of this so called 'Progress'. There comes a time when you have to decide whether to continue living in the ignorance of eventuality or end the chapter right there. Every entity in this universe has a lifespan within which it is allowed to prosper and grow. The flag on the other side of the river, the arch at the end of the journey, it is there for a reason. If you try to extend it, expect more from it, the entity ceases to be what it originally was and becomes something foul, something ugly.
